
					// Grasscutter 3.4.0 GM Handbook// Created 2023/02/01 19:05:18// Commands account : Modify user accounts announce : Send announcement to all online players, or manage server'sannouncement ban : Ban a player clear : Deletes unequipped unlocked items from your inventory. Defaults to4* level 1 refinement 1 or lower, but can be set higher. coop : Forces someone to join the world of others. If no one is targeted,it sends you into co-op mode anyway. enter_dungeon : Enter a dungeon give : Gives an item to you or the specified player. Can also give allweapons, avatars and/or materials, and can construct custom artifacts. heal : Heal all characters in your current team. help : Sends the help message or shows information about a specifiedcommand kick : Kicks the specified player from the server (WIP) killall : Kill all entities killCharacter : Kills the players current character language : Display or change current language list : List online players permission : Grants or removes a permission for a user position : Gets position and rotation information quest : Add or finish quests reload : Reload server config resetConst : Resets the constellation level on your current active character,you will need to relog after using the command to see any changesresetShopLimit : Reset target player's shop refresh time sendMail : Sends mail to the specified user. The usage of this commandchanges based on its composition state sendMessage : Sends a message to a player as the server. If used with no target,sends to all players on the server. setConst : Sets constellation level for your current active charactersetFetterLevel : Sets your fetter level for your current active character setProp : Sets accountwide properties. Things like godmode can be enabledthis way, as well as changing things like unlocked abyss floor and battle passprogress. Values for <prop> (case-insensitive): GodMode |UnlimitedStamina | UnlimitedEnergy | TowerLevel | WorldLevel | BPLevel |SetOpenState | UnsetOpenState | UnlockMap (cont.) see PlayerProperty enum for other possible values, ofthe form PROP_MAX_SPRING_VOLUME -> max_spring_volume setStats : Sets fight property for your current active character Values for <stat>: hp | maxhp | def | atk | em | er | crate |cdmg | cdr | heal | heali | shield | defi (cont.) Elemental DMG Bonus: epyro | ecryo | ehydro | egeo |edendro | eelectro | ephys (cont.) Elemental RES: respyro | rescryo | reshydro | resgeo |resdendro | reselectro | resphys spawn : Spawns an entity near you stop : Stops the server talent : Set talent level for your current active character team : Modify your team manually. teleport : Change the player's position teleportAll : Teleports all players in your world to your position unban : Unban a player unlockall : Unlocks all open states for a player. weather : Changes weather ID and climate type. Weather IDs can be foundin ./Resources/ExcelBinOutput/WeatherExcelConfigData.json. Climate types: sunny, cloudy, rain, thunderstorm, snow, mist windy : This value does not exist. Please report this to the Discord:commands.windy.description// Avatars10000001 : Kate10000002 : Kamisato Ayaka10000003 : Jean10000005 : Traveler10000006 : Lisa10000007 : Traveler10000014 :
